Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.28,0:00:14.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong lakukan sesuatu soal ini, Kapten.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pernah melihat gejala ini sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.97,0:00:19.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hapyneth.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.02,0:00:23.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.00,0:00:25.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kalian bertemu belakangan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.97,0:00:35.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan cari alasan misi dari guild lagi\Nsupaya bisa mengajak Hapyneth dan Cecilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, kenapa tidak diajak kencan saja\Nseperti biasa?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.06,0:00:42.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke-Kencan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.37,0:00:47.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Punya dua atasan yang bahkan tidak berani\Nmengajak kencan gadis yang mereka sukai...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.95,0:00:49.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sungguh malang.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.77,0:00:52.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ba-Baiklah...!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktunya melaksanakan
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.01,0:00:58.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Operasi Terapi Kejut Raven\NLewat Kencan Grup"!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Langit cerah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuacanya bagus, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.68,0:02:38.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita semangat\Ndan main sepuasnya hari ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.84,0:02:42.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Duke. Sejak kapan\Nkau jadi akrab dengan Irene?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.84,0:02:46.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu aku bilang ini\Nuntuk menghibur Kapten,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,katanya dia mau membantu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.12,0:02:49.60,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak sabar.\NAku ingin makan sesuatu yang lezat.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, ayo kita berangkat!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, hari ini kita mau ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.42,0:03:00.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena Hapyneth punya tempat\Nyang ingin dikunjungi, kita ke sana dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.62,0:03:02.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat ingin.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita mau pergi ke tempat wisata\Nyang baru buka itu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.35,0:03:06.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tepat sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.84,0:03:10.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempat wisata yang baru buka?\NJangan-jangan...!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.16,0:03:17.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mau.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlalu dini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempat itu pasti sangat ramai,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.60,0:03:33.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan kalau kita ke sana,\Nbisa-bisa malah jadi keributan,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi sebaiknya jangan hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jebol.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah ini luar biasa?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.10,0:03:56.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya Raja membangun ini\Nuntuk merayakan penaklukan Raja Iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mirip sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.36,0:04:08.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak perlu sungkan. Aku bangga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya mantap juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Operasinya sukses besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hapyneth.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada krim di pipimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Komandan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga, itu memang Komandan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi suara yang tadi itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.02,0:04:36.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.26,0:04:44.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf. Ini pertama kalinya\Naku mendengar suara Tuan Raven,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.22,0:04:47.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku sedikit terkejut.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurang ajar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.20,0:04:56.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih atas kerja kerasnya,\NWakil Komandan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Komandan sedang libur hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.10,0:05:02.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, jangan khawatirkan kami\Ndan silakan lanjut berpatroli.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Tak kusangka kau sampai dilindungi
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.31,0:05:06.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,bukan hanya oleh bawahanmu,\Ntapi juga oleh wanita lemah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.76,0:05:11.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan nikmati waktu istirahat Anda,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.63,0:05:12.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Raven.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu... Komandan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raven.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.46,0:05:31.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Raven!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan segera menjemputnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.90,0:05:34.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga ikut.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.36,0:05:40.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu dia syok,\Ntapi tak kusangka sampai kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.16,0:05:45.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya ada kesatria yang dari awal\Ntidak puas dengan komandan yang pendiam,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.11,0:05:50.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi yang mengumpulkan mereka\Nuntuk membuat faksi itu si Wakil Komandan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku orang baru di sini,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi kemampuanku\Nuntuk bantu-bantu juga ada batasnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata hidupmu berat juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.03,0:05:59.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sebelah sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kucing-kucingannya sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita kembali ke tempat teman-teman.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk apa kembali\Nsetelah melihatku seperti ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi Anda kabur karena malu terlihat payah?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.91,0:06:18.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anda berniat untuk tidak\Nmenemui Hapyneth selamanya, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.66,0:06:22.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kupikir ini bukan ide yang buruk\Nkarena Hapyneth bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.60,0:06:24.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kecewa padamu!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.96,0:06:30.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dibilang begini saja masih diam,\Nya sudahlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.50,0:06:31.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sisanya kuserahkan padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.63,0:06:37.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhir-akhir ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.26,0:06:43.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku benar-benar menyadari kelemahan\Ndan ketidakmampuanku sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Misi di laut itu,\Nkau pasti masih ingat, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.03,0:06:50.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu itu Hapyneth bilang
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,bahwa dia punya rahasia.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.04,0:06:56.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia juga terlihat\Nseperti sedang ketakutan akan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.76,0:06:58.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti itu adalah hal yang sangat serius.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,apakah orang sepertiku\Nyang selalu bimbang ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,mampu menanggung rahasia miliknya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan soal suaraku pun selalu begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya terus melarikan diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.23,0:07:15.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Andai saja aku sepertimu,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,punya keberanian untuk\Nmendekati orang yang kusuka...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.00,0:07:20.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.57,0:07:24.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pikir aku ini siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.90,0:07:27.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ini cuma cowok pecundang\Nyang saking malunya,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.16,0:07:30.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,malah pakai topeng saat jalan berduaan\Nsama cewek yang kusuka!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raven, bangkitlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.46,0:07:36.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kaki itu cuma pajangan?\NBukan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak mungkin selemah itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.86,0:07:43.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu karena aku, Duke, dan juga Hapyneth...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami semua percaya padamu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.80,0:07:52.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semangatmu yang aneh itu\Nselalu bisa memberiku kekuatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf karena sudah bertindak egois.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumaafkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.66,0:08:15.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, karena kucing-kucingan\NKomandan sudah selesai,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.16,0:08:18.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,selanjutnya ayo kita belanja!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kedengarannya menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hapyneth.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.03,0:08:29.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin aku orang\Nyang kurang bisa diandalkan, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.46,0:08:32.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan berusaha agar suatu saat nanti\Nkau mau menceritakan rahasiamu padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.83,0:08:35.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dimengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.56,0:08:40.50,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Youki!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa, Cecilia?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.66,0:08:47.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hapyneth menghilang!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.46,0:08:53.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menerima surat pengajuan\Ncuti panjang dari Hapyneth, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada pesan misterius tertulis di atasnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bahasa Hapyneth yang biasanya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudnya ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.48,0:09:07.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya,\Njemput dia di hutan satu bulan lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hutan mana yang dia maksud?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau soal itu, sepertinya aku tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hapyneth pasti punya\Npertimbangannya sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Hapy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.63,0:09:26.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Halo.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.10,0:09:30.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga, jangan buat orang melacakmu\Npakai penguat indra penciuman.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepercayaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, semuanya mengkhawatirkanmu, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.98,0:09:38.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah membulatkan tekad.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kusampaikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepadanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentang diriku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau serius?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.83,0:09:52.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau Raven sampai tidak bisa menerimanya,\Nkau akan kehilangan segalanya, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.86,0:09:54.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.86,0:09:59.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, hubunganmu dengan Kapten\Ndan kami juga bakal diselidiki.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau sampai itu terjadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takkan merepotkan kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.90,0:10:06.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan cuma soal merepotkan lagi, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku, Shiek, bahkan Kapten sekalipun.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.83,0:10:12.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua yang sudah kita dapatkan sejak datang\Nke Minerva bisa hilang begitu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, kalau Hapyneth yang pintar...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah tahu hal seperti ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.46,0:10:22.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa berbohong lagi.\NAku ingin katakan padanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semangat, Kak Hapy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.06,0:10:31.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiek...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini hal yang penting buat Kak Hapy, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.97,0:10:38.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku akan mendukungmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Duke juga begitu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Betul.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.96,0:10:48.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tekadmu sudah sebulat itu,\Njangan khawatirkan kami dan lakukanlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.00,0:10:50.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.30,0:10:53.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapten juga bilang sesuatu, dong.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.50,0:10:57.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua sudah selesaikan\Ndengan baik...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya tak ada lagi\Nyang perlu kukatakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak berguna.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.00,0:11:05.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bercanda, Kapten.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.64,0:11:06.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.76,0:11:18.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata Tuan Raven.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kabar kesehatan Anda hari ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.43,0:11:22.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada masalah dengan kesehatanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suara tadi itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.00,0:11:26.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tidak sopan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau memanggilku dengan nama saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak sebodoh itu
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.43,0:11:35.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk membiarkan seseorang\Nyang tidak tahu tata krama
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan mengganggu ketertiban ordo kesatria
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,tetap menduduki posisi Wakil Komandan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.20,0:11:44.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksud perkataan Anda, Tuan Raven?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.90,0:11:46.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Panggil aku Komandan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan kelancangan saya, Komandan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.63,0:12:14.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak Hapyneth pergi,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,sepertinya sudah hampir satu bulan, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Hapyneth benar-benar berencana...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Persis seperti yang kau bayangkan, Cecilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.03,0:12:27.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Duke pasti sudah memandu Raven\Nke tempat Hapyneth sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.76,0:12:33.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rupanya Youki berkunjung, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.63,0:12:34.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah dibahas, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal perjodohanmu itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.43,0:12:43.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki sedang kesulitan\Nkarena urusan temannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.96,0:12:46.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak ingin memberinya\Nbeban pikiran tambahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.78,0:12:51.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yakin? Calonmu sudah datang ke Minerva, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat atau lambat\NYouki juga akan tahu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya menerima perjodohan ini\Natas perintah Raja.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.36,0:13:00.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu aku bertemu dengannya,\Naku akan langsung menolak.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi Cecilia,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.46,0:13:07.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,bagaimana perasaanmu terhadap Youki?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.46,0:13:10.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki tak ada hubungannya\Ndengan masalah ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.70,0:13:15.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pokoknya, jangan membahas\Ntentang perjodohan tanpa seizinku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.00,0:13:19.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rupanya kau sedikit menaksir dia, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.57,0:13:22.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan begitu. Makanya...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.63,0:13:23.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar bodoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau benar-benar tak ada hubungannya,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.62,0:13:29.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau takkan berniat\Nmerahasiakan perjodohan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.03,0:13:54.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini milik Hapyneth...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ikutlah denganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi pada Hapyneth?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki, aku harus menebasmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku menaruh harapan padamu,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku kecewa.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harusnya aku yang bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan, kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak perlu kujelaskan!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jelaskan padaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.83,0:14:32.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini balasan karena menyakiti Hapyneth.\NTerima ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kubilang tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.96,0:14:50.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia jadi lebih kuat dari sebelumnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, itu wujud aslimu yang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau apakan Hapyneth?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.06,0:15:22.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raven.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada gunanya bicara!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.76,0:15:31.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah, hentikan ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.74,0:15:34.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Endless Dark!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang kau mengerti, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.86,0:15:51.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raven, kau takkan bisa menang dariku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku takkan menyerah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa sampai sejauh ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.83,0:15:59.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya apa yang terjadi\Nantara kau dan Hapyneth?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah berjanji.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.63,0:16:05.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi menyamar jadi manusia,\Nkau mencabut semua bulunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.86,0:16:08.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makanya, dia memintaku menghajarmu sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.90,0:16:11.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, begitulah ceritanya.\NKita mulai.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bercanda!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ditebas pedang itu sekali saja,\Naku bisa mati, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah... Kalau begitu, begini saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kupukul dengan sisi tumpulnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu pedang bermata dua!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.33,0:16:39.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hapyneth!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tet-teret!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.63,0:16:50.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bercandamu itu sudah keterlaluan, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyesal.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.76,0:16:55.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kalian berdua...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.50,0:17:01.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,bagaimana akhirnya bisa berbaikan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat aku dipandu Duke ke sebuah hutan...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.85,0:17:09.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai dari sini\Nkau harus pergi sendiri, Raven.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.43,0:17:13.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Duke?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.96,0:17:15.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jawaban untuk Hapyneth,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,sampaikanlah langsung\Ndari mulutmu sendiri, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.06,0:17:23.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hapyneth?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hapyneth, kau ada di sana?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau bersembunyi?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.56,0:17:37.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau membawaku ke sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.37,0:17:42.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sini adalah tempat\Nsegalanya bermula bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.40,0:17:47.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serta, tempat segalanya berakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempat yang penuh kenangan, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.63,0:17:56.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raven, aku senang bisa bertemu denganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menghabiskan waktu bersamamu\Nsangatlah menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika bisa, aku ingin bersamamu selamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan. Jangan mendekat!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.90,0:18:29.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takut bahwa semuanya\Ntetap berada dalam kepalsuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.26,0:18:33.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, jika aku memikirkan bahwa semua ini
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.66,0:18:35.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan berakhir...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.96,0:18:42.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.36,0:18:51.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raven?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku karena\Ntak menyadarinya lebih awal.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pasti sangat menderita selama ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak membenciku?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.66,0:19:03.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku menyukaimu, Hapyneth.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.43,0:19:08.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu belum cukup jadi alasan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, aku juga
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.00,0:19:13.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,suka.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,tidak apa-apa, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.90,0:19:19.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manis banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlalu manis!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.46,0:19:37.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan lebih manis\Ndari gula kotak di rumah Cecilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.73,0:19:44.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian sudah dapat akhir yang bahagia,\Ntapi malah bercanda ingin menghajarku?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.10,0:19:50.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kuberikan "hadiah" perayaan dariku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saint Chain!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.06,0:19:54.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lepaskan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, aku pasang\Npenghalang pengusir monster juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Nselamat menikmati waktu berdua!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seandainya terjadi sesuatu\Nyang buruk pada Raven dan yang lain,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan sulit bagi kita\Nuntuk minum teh bersama seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.76,0:20:17.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cecilia?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.23,0:20:25.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku akan sedikit sibuk\Nsetelah ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.30,0:20:27.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu untuk minum teh\Nmungkin akan berkurang.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.56,0:20:30.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, tapi cuma sebentar, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.16,0:20:32.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm? Ah, jangan dipikirkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan ada di Minerva\Nuntuk sementara waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.00,0:20:39.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Si Yuuga memintaku membantu sebuah tugas,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.42,0:20:42.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku harus pergi ke suatu pertambangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bilang ini sangat mendesak.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin akan memakan waktu\Nsekitar dua sampai tiga minggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak kusangka kau sudah akrab\Ndengan Yuuga juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.30,0:20:58.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.56,0:21:00.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Youki ada di dalam?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.19,0:21:04.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan Youki pada kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tangkap! Ringkus!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki, kau berulah apa lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian yang duluan cari gara-gara, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih tehnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.10,0:21:22.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan datang lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan kabur kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.50,0:21:27.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habisi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Janji, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.63,0:21:34.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, kita juga pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.06,0:22:02.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hapyneth, aku ikut senang!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.83,0:22:10.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi berutang budi sangat besar\Npada Youki.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.81,0:22:13.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapten, terima kasih.
